Errors: Method SM 2320 B-1997(2011) : The upper control limit was exceeded for one or more analytes in the Continuing Calibration Verification (CCV). The field samples analyzed in this sequence did not contain the analyte(s) in question above the Method Reporting Limit (MRL). Since the exceedance equates to a potential high bias the data quality was not significantly affected and no further corrective action was taken.
No significant anomalies were noted with this analysis.
